(8, '<p style="text-align:center;line-height:3em;"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:14px;line-height:3em;text-align:left;"><br /></span></p><p style="text-align:left;line-height:2em;"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:14px;line-height:3em;text-align:left;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:16px;line-height:3em;text-align:left;">琅琅乾坤，沧桑正道。成人之美，善莫大焉。成人之美事乏有，猎头顾问乃成人美事之凤麟。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:left;line-height:2em;"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:16px;line-height:3em;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;猎头顾问助人才成材，跃人才通财，擢人才荣耀；辅企业幸得驰驹良将，促企业品质上阶，财路亨通，效益层楼更上，事业腾达飞黄；结缘天下英雄、世间富商、学苑宗师，引俊彦畅行，领豪贾攀峰，扶巨匠翱翔。猎头顾问乃芸芸英中之翘楚，社会发展润通之卓秀。</span></p><p style="text-align:left;line-height:2em;"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:16px;line-height:3em;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;腾驹达涉游猎头服务，纵览东西，独特的视野、超尘的风采、卓然的气度、精妙的渐悟、无双的理念，循序提升着行业的品质和品位。缘此，高级猎头顾问云集，腾驹达秀类拔萃，诱人入胜。</span></p><p style="line-height:2em;"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:16px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;加盟腾驹达猎头顾问之群魁，乃经营社会资源之开端，迈向新成功之初步，润通社会之契机。崭新未来呼唤您：刷新昨日优势，创造明天灿烂，铺就今生康荣大道。</span></p><p style="line-height:3em;text-align:center;margin-top:25px;"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:14px;line-height:3em;text-align:right;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:14px;line-height:3em;text-align:right;">——</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:14px;line-height:3em;text-align:right;">景素奇于二零零三年</span></p>', '2013-12-24', '管理员', 1, '人才服务-品味猎头'),
(9, '<p style="text-align:left;line-height:4em;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><br /></span></p><p style="text-align:left;line-height:4em;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、高端人才自己登门找工作，雇主方会心存疑虑；</span></p><p style="line-height:4em;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、人才本身达到一定的高度后，不再愿亲自出面找工作，</span></p><p style="line-height:4em;"><span style="line-height:3em;font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:16px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 被雇主方盘问个没完没了，觉得很没有面子；</span></p><p style="line-height:4em;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、人才自身的信息渠道十分有限；</span></p><p style="line-height:4em;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4、非常希望了解雇主职位的真实性、有效性；</span></p><p style="line-height:4em;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5、特别高端的人才需要猎头顾问帮助从中穿针引线，</span></p><p style="line-height:4em;"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 对双方的期望进行平衡协调管理。</span></p><br /><p style="text-align:left;line-height:4em;"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:14px;line-height:5em;"></span></p>', '2013-12-25', '管理员', 1, '人才服务-人才为什么选择猎头'),
